what_worked: Applied early_filter, pushdown, materialize_cte: Created CTEs for filtered dimension tables (date_dim, store, household_demographics) to push down filters early, then joined with store_sales for aggregation before final customer join. Converted implicit joins to explicit JOIN syntax.
why_it_worked: Applying selective filters early reduces intermediate row counts before expensive operations; Pushing predicates closer to table scans reduces data volume in upper operators; Materializing a CTE used multiple times prevents redundant re-computation
